name: Attorney General Josh Kaul
tweet: This decision creates significant uncertainty and, unfortunately, will mean more taxpayer dollars wasted in redistricting litigation. We need a nonpartisan redistricting process in Wisconsin.

name: Attorney General Josh Kaul
tweet: Today’s shocking ruling is inconsistent with the reasoning of other recent rulings from the Supreme Court, but it is consistent with the increasing judicial activism we’ve seen from the Court’s conservative super majority.
